4️⃣ ELIGIBILITY PROGRESS
(Truth Ladder Engine)
Eligibility ≠ automatic upgrade.
It measures maturity.

L0 → L1 Eligibility
Conditions (example):
    • ≥ 10 completed tests
    • ≥ 30 active students
    • Difficulty tagging coverage ≥ 90%
UI:
Progress bar
“7 / 10 Tests Completed”

L1 → L2 Eligibility
Conditions:
    • ≥ 25 diagnostic runs
    • Phase adherence metric computed
    • Behavioral variance computed
Checklist UI:
✔ Diagnostic depth available
✔ Minimum run volume achieved
⬜ Behavioral variance threshold

L2 → L3 Eligibility
Invitation-only.
UI:
“Governance Tier available by evaluation.”
Optional show:
    • Stability Index ≥ 70
    • ≥ 1 academic year completed
No self-upgrade button.

